## Python
```Python
# for n <= 4
def A(n,w="12"):
    if len(w) > (2*n+1)*n: return 2
    return sum(A(n, w+t) for t in "123456789"[:2*n+1]
        if t!=w[-1] and t+w[-1] not in w and w[-1]+t not in w)
```
